Programming the Atmega1284p:
Using 'Butler Fund 2008' FT232 serial bit banger (ECE 477)
===============================================
|   FT232   |      1284p      |     VCC/GND   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 1	    |	 Pin 6	   |	  ---	   |	// MOSI		-- DTR - data terminal ready 
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 2	    |	 Pin 8	   |	  ---	   |	// SCK 		-- CLOCK (rts) - request to send
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 3	    |	 Pin 9	   |	  ---	   |	// RESET	-- !txd - held low
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 11   |	 Pin 7      |	  ---	   |	// MISO		-- cts - clear to send
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 20   |	  ---	   |	VCC	   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  Pin 21   |	  --- 	   |	GND	   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|    ---	    |	Pin 10	   |	VCC	   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|    ---	    |  	Pin 11	   |	GND	   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|    ---	    |	Pin 30	   |	VCC	   |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|    ---	    |	Pin 31	   |	GND	   |
===============================================